{"word":"G2647 - καταλύω - katalýō - kat-al-oo'-o - Destroy","slug":"G2647","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταλύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>katalýō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kat-al-oo'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Destroy"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x03BB;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - kataluo&#x0304;</b> - <i>kat-al-oo'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G3089\">G3089</a>; to <i>loosen down</i> (<i>disintegrate</i>), that is, (by implication) to <i>demolish</i> (literally or figuratively); specifically (compare <a href=\"#/G2646\">G2646</a>) to <i>halt</i> for the night: - destroy, dissolve, be guest, lodge, come to nought, overthrow, throw down."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G179\">G179</a>, <a href=\"#/G1955\">G1955</a>, <a href=\"#/G1956\">G1956</a>, <a href=\"#/G2646\">G2646</a>, <a href=\"#/G3083\">G3083</a>, <a href=\"#/G3084\">G3084</a>, <a href=\"#/G3085\">G3085</a>, <a href=\"#/G3086\">G3086</a>, <a href=\"#/G3089\">G3089</a>, <a href=\"#/G359\">G359</a>, <a href=\"#/G360\">G360</a>, <a href=\"#/G487\">G487</a>, <a href=\"#/G629\">G629</a>, <a href=\"#/G630\">G630</a>"}]}